translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,104,"Futhi awuwuceli umvuzo kubona ngakho, akuyilutho ngaphandle kokuthi kuyisikhumbuzo emihlabeni"
  12,105,Futhi zingaphi izimpawu emazulwini nasemhlabeni abazidlulayo kulapho bona bengazinakile na
  12,106,Futhi iningi labo alikholwa kuMvelinqangi ngaphandle kokuthi bona bangabenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni
  12,107,Ngakube bazizwa bephephile yini ukuthi bangafikelwa isijeziso esimangalisayo esivela kuMvelinqangi noma ukuthi bafikelwe ihora ngokuphazima kweso kulapho bona bengaboni (benganakile) na
  12,108,"Ithi, “lena indlela yami ngimemela kuMvelinqangi ngolwazi mina kanye nalabo abangilandelayo futhi udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi futhi mina angisiyena omunye wabakhonzi bezithixo”"
  12,109,Futhi asizange sithumela muntu ngaphambilini kwakho ngaphandle kwamadoda esembula kuwona isambulo okungabantu bamadolobha ngakube abazange yini bahambe ezweni babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo futhi ikhaya lempilo ezayo lingcono kulabo abenza okulungileyo ngakube aninamqondo yini na
  12,110,"Kwaze kwaba ilapho izithunywa ziphela khona amandla futhi zacabanga ukuthi zona zaziphikwa, usizo lwethu lwafika kuzona ngakho-ke basindiswa labo esibathandayo futhi angeke siqhelelaniswe isijeziso sethu nabantu abayizoni"
  12,111,Ngempela emilandweni yabo kunesifundo kubantu abaqondayo (iQur’an) akusiyona inkulumo eqanjiwe kepha igcwalisela lokho okwakungaphambilini kwayo nencazelo ngobunjalo bazo zonke izinto nokuhola nomusa kubantu abakholwayo